ClimaCast License Agreement

Version 1.0

Effective Date: [Insert Date]

1. Grant of License
All rights to the content provided by ClimaCast are owned exclusively by the creator. By accessing ClimaCast, you acknowledge and agree that you are granted a non-exclusive, non-transferable license to view the content for informational purposes only. This license does not grant you any rights to modify, distribute, or exploit the content in any way.

2. Permissions
You may:

View the content of ClimaCast solely for your personal use.

3. Restrictions
You may not:

Copy, reproduce, modify, or create derivative works based on any content from ClimaCast in any format or media.

Use, distribute, share, or sell any ClimaCast content for personal, educational, commercial, or any other purposes without prior written permission from the creator.

Publicly display, perform, or distribute any ClimaCast content in any manner that would violate copyright or intellectual property laws.

Use any automated systems, scripts, or tools to extract, collect, or harvest data or content from ClimaCast.

Remove or alter any copyright or proprietary notices on any content from ClimaCast.

4. Ownership
All content, including but not limited to text, images, graphics, software, code, and multimedia elements, is the property of ClimaCast and is protected by copyright, trademark, and other intellectual property laws. Your use of ClimaCast does not grant you any ownership rights or intellectual property rights in any of the content.

5. Disclaimer
ClimaCast provides weather forecasts and information as a service. While efforts are made to ensure the accuracy of the information provided, ClimaCast does not guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or reliability of any content. You acknowledge that any reliance on the information provided by ClimaCast is at your own risk. ClimaCast shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or special damages arising from the use of or inability to use the content.

6. Termination
This license is effective until terminated by either party. You may terminate this license at any time by ceasing all use of ClimaCast content. ClimaCast reserves the right to terminate this license immediately and without notice if you violate any of its terms. Upon termination, all rights granted to you under this license will cease, and you must destroy all copies of ClimaCast content in your possession.

7. Governing Law
This license shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of [Your Country/Region]. Any disputes arising from this license shall be resolved in the competent courts of the United Kingdom.
